snippet.title: Gal Gadot & Dwayne Johnson Play “Is This Valuable Art?”
snippet.description:
Dwayne and Gal talk about their daughters, Gal not getting a baby gift from Dwayne or Ryan Reynolds, and since their new movie Red Notice is about art heists, we put their knowledge to the test in a round of “Is This Valuable Art?”
